Program: Great Lives
Title: John D Rockefeller
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00glwz3
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 May 2005
Martin Smith, the Chairman of English National Opera proposes John D Rockefeller, the founder of Standard Oil; a man who was both simultaneously incredibly rich, extremely hated and a great philanthropist. Francine Stock presents.